The paper discusses the notion of optimality in the context of strategic games, CP-nets, and soft constraints, which are all topics related to game theory, artificial intelligence, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems).
